Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:19.33,sign_3370_33_The_Rising_of_th,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,645)}The Rising of the Shield Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:36.32,sign_5367_37_Lullaby_at_Dawn,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(486,682)}The Savior of the Heavenly Fowl
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:38.20,flashbackitalics,G,0000,0000,0000,,I've received an order for \Nherbicide, Shield Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:42.03,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,A village to the south needs \Na lot of it, and immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:46.96,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one I can ask. \NYou have the Heavenly Fowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:51.42,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why would they need herbicide \Nso quickly, and so much of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:55.46,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master, the plants here are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:03.06,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you'd definitely \Nneed herbicide for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:05.68,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Naofumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:10.31,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Take us there, Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:12.19,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:18.82,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.49,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,This place was about to \Nfall to the vines, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:24.70,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you have burned them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:28.33,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,We tried everything we could think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:32.04,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,We even summoned adventurers,\Nbut the situation remains grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:35.88,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Our village was already overrun by vines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:39.97,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,What's worse, the plants turned \Ninto monsters and attacked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.19,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Turned into monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:49.48,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Some adventurers set out for \Nthe village to level up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:51.31,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to stop them, but to no avail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:55.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo, grab the adventurers \Nand bring them back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:59.49,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Be wighd bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:07.75,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Plant monsters were all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:11.50,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Some even spat poison or acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.88,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Why would these guys go \Nthere when they're so weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:16.21,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,They must be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:18.35,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to say that last part.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:19.79,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:21.38,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "huh" me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:22.51,top,F,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:24.55,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that bird that talked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:24.14,top,R,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "ugh" me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.26,top,F,0000,0000,0000,,Tch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:25.26,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:27.97,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,That has to be the Heavenly Fowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.98,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,The Savior of the Heavenly Fowl \Nhas come to our village, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:36.32,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the savior who travels in a carriage \Ndrawn by a heavenly fowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.82,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You've got the wrong guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.44,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:40.89,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,We beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:44.41,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please heal our \Nsick using your powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.49,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, some of you are sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:55.04,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, the plants are \Ndevouring their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:58.09,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,They're even parasitic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:02.01,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Savior! Help them with your powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.97,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say for sure that \NI'll be able to heal them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:11.60,sign_12611_112_Potion_Enhance,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(104,1)}Potion Enhance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:22.61,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:23.20,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:26.49,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad it went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:27.32,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:30.08,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But we're leaving as soon as \Nwe get paid for the treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:32.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be dragged \Nany further into this mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.63,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I daresay that might be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:40.25,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Our Savior of the Heavenly Fowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:42.76,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Please save our village!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:51.60,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Our village was being ravaged by \Nfamine when the Spear Hero visited.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.10,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,When he heard of our plight,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:05:00.07,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,he went to some nearby ruins and brought \Nback a seed that had been sealed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:04.82,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,He called it a miracle seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:07.11,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,A miracle seed that was sealed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.49,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That was it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:16.29,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,At first, we were overjoyed when we saw how \Nquickly the plants grew and bore fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.57,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:21.30,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,They grew too much and \Noverwhelmed your village?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.34,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.55,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,While investigating our options,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:27.51,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,we hit upon a legend \Npassed down the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:32.60,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, an alchemist who'd set \Nup shop in this area created a seed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:35.01,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,but sealed it away for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:41.23,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,The legend also said that plants had \Novertaken the region for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.82,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:46.97,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why did none of you have doubts about \Nthat seed if you knew about this legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:53.12,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You convinced yourself it was safe \Nbecause a hero brought it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:06:01.63,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,We'll pay for treatments, and for \Nthe monster extermination, in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:04.84,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Please save our village!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:11.51,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like cleaning up \Nafter that moron Motoyasu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:13.60,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll earn my keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:18.98,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,That shield... Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:20.31,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:49.05,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Take that thing out, and it'll all be over?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.47,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it's that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:53.76,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:55.89,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:58.93,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Air Strike Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:14.53,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It regenerates too quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.79,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,If normal attacks won't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:17.49,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.96,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Splash this herbicide \Ndirectly on that eyeball.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:20.75,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.46,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:24.42,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.97,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold me back, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:37.10,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.18,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:46.44,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just laugh, Filo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.11,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,No, I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.24,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that. Get the herbicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:51.95,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,"Never mind"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:01.37,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Regenerating again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.83,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:07.75,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,If the Potion Enhance skill works \Non the herbicide as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:13.34,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away, Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:28.52,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:32.03,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,This is what the Shield Hero can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.36,sign_14108_106_Potion_Enhance,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(104,1)}Potion Enhance
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.08,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:51.09,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Get back, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.73,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Those seeds could cause more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:07.27,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's gather them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.74,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That one was mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.95,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I got it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.53,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:18.41,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,No, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.24,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.29,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.12,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.08,sign_15364_118_Bio_Plant_Shield,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(151,1)}Bio Plant Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:29.34,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Plant Modification?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:46.14,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:50.52,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I unlocked a skill called Plant Modification,\N so I tried a little experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:55.53,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We just barely took down that monster, \Nso please don't be so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:03.74,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Our Savior... \NNo, Shield Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:06.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I exterminated the monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:09.08,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You guys clean up the \Nwithered vines yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:10.58,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:11.92,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired. I'm going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.13,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.56,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.10,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:33.61,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to get a read on \Nthe Shield Hero, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:34.86,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:38.15,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,He's so quiet and cool, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:40.32,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh... right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:48.04,sign_17314_135_Plant_Analysis_S,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(194,1)}Plant Analysis Skill Unlocked
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:54.55,sign_17400_136_Bio_Plant_Seed,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(275,1)}Bio Plant Seed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:56.21,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.51,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.93,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You can sleep some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.89,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:06.56,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a seed from yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:08.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wait and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:12.19,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, please don't take such risks...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.53,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:27.16,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Those look yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:31.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I curbed their breeding \Nand mutation potential,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:33.67,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,then increased their growth and productivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:37.71,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,With this, they should bear lots of edible \Nfruit without turning into monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:38.63,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The village will never have \Nto worry about famine again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:44.05,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Sir Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:46.68,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did you save us from danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:49.18,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,you're giving us such a wonderful gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.14,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Who said anything about {\i1}giving{\i0} it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:53.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's cut a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:54.61,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sell you these seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.94,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,For the right price, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:59.36,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You're too greedy, Naofumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:04.99,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,B-But we paid everything we had for \Nthe treatment and extermination.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:07.24,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You can also exchange goods for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:10.62,main,C,0000,0000,0000,,What? But we have nothing left...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:15.42,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.30,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys are really tough-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.63,top,F,0000,0000,0000,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:20.46,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We have so much fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:23.09,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,most of it will rot before we can eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:25.80,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I know someone \Nwe can sell it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:30.14,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,This seed certainly is very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:33.64,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gladly buy it all, \Nincluding the produce.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.23,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We have a deal, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:40.15,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,You placed several attractive products \Nin sight to create an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:43.20,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,You truly are a shining example \Nof the trader's spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:44.95,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:45.78,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:49.49,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't busy, could I request \Nyour assistance with a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:56.46,flashbackitalics,G,0000,0000,0000,,There's a hot springs town \Nnot too far away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:59.67,flashbackitalics,G,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to deliver some \Ngoods to an inn there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:03.42,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,Great. The order is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:04.72,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:09.39,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,There are hot springs towns \Nin this world, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:13.10,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,So warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.35,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:17.48,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go in this hot spring thing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.52,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hot spring, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:20.86,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Raphtalia?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:25.03,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not {\i1}that{\i0} interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:29.03,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But if you and Filo want \Nto go, I'll accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:32.95,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's that. We're spending the night here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.12,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.62,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.46,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I wuv you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:47.93,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy that we're staying \Nin a hot springs inn,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:51.06,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,but Filo's being too clingy \Nwith Naofumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:53.68,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be clingy with him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:03.07,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,"The origin of this hot spring,\N and its benefits"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.99,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What does a silver boar have \Nto do with a hot spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.45,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:11.83,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Its effects are... success in love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:16.75,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,"A couple that enters this hot spring \Ntogether will be united forever"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:22.00,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, if I can take a b-bath \Ntogether with Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.30,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:30.05,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We can't k-k-kiss! I'll get pregnant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.85,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, an open-air bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.31,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:41.27,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,So big!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo, don't swim in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.19,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:48.86,top,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is that okay in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:51.78,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering why Filo wasn't here yet,\Nand she's with Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:54.58,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You swim too, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.87,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.79,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Then wash my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.67,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you do it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:09.80,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, Filo was with \NNaofumi-sama the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:14.89,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I want to share this drink with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:18.27,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,That feels good, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:21.98,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You have way too much hair. \NBrushing it is a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:23.31,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:26.61,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia had much shorter hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:29.53,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,I wish he'd brush my hair too, like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.28,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:33.87,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:35.95,top,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:37.16,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sit still,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.00,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,or I won't brush your hair again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:42.54,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,No! It feels good, so keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:45.04,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Also, do my feathers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.84,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Do your wings yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:49.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Raphtalia?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.88,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.68,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, gimme.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:10.19,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do something, or Filo \Nwill steal my Naofumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:17.33,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,If I want to turn this around all at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:27.84,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,Mom used to say that a gift was the best \Nway to get your beloved's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:32.68,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,She fell in love with Dad after \Nhe gave her a gift, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:40.77,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,If I can give him some latium...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:43.64,flashback,W,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you heard of latium?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:46.56,flashback,W,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean that rare \Ncrystal found in this area?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:51.07,flashback,W,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, love charms made \Nwith it work really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:52.82,flashback,W,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:55.95,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,A bird called a gagocco collects latium,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.41,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,so if I find one of their nests,\NI'll get my hands on some!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:03.21,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I'll give it to Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:06.88,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,W-We mustn't, Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.34,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, if we kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.00,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:11.96,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:13.67,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Filo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.39,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she up in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.43,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,Is she after the latium, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:21.22,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You're here for the eggs too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:22.02,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:24.60,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,The old man at the inn told me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:28.15,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,that the eggs of a bird called \Na gagocco are a rare delicacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:31.11,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's just being a glutton like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.99,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,She's still such a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:37.16,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,If I take a rare delicacy to Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:41.29,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll pet me and become my mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:43.00,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:44.87,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,Mating means marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.87,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Filo's thinking that far ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:50.50,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,So I won't let you have the eggs, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.30,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:18:00.72,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Eggs, eggs, yummy eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:05.52,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,When did this become a race?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.48,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You're so slow, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.52,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:21.78,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:24.08,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:26.37,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:28.87,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:34.25,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's good that this thing \Ncushioned our fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.31,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:49.85,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, get on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:04.83,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,That was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:08.04,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.87,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're even, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:13.84,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:20.97,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,So that's a gagocco and its nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.43,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Eggs, eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:33.69,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.98,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I just really need that crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:51.25,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,My eggs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:59.01,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:00.22,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:18.28,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we didn't find \Nany other gagocco nests.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:25.91,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,Will giving Naofumi-sama this \Nthing instead make him happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:28.20,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:32.29,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a silver razorback?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:33.42,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:34.71,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Like that thing over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.84,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:38.59,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Could you give it to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:44.18,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Silver razorbacks are valuable prey, \Nused as offerings in town rituals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:46.64,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Please! We'll pay good money for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:48.51,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:49.97,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:54.10,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:56.23,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Filo and I picked it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:59.65,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We thought you might want a \Ntool to help you craft metals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:00.82,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:03.78,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But wasn't this pretty expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:10.24,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's a token of our gratitude to you, \Nfor always taking such good care of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:13.16,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. A gift for you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:17.21,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I'll make good use of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:19.17,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:23.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, go take a \Ndip in the hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.23,0:21:30.89,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,He still treats me like a child at times,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:35.81,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll make him recognize \Nmy womanly charms one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:37.41,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Filo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:39.77,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:15.41,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Godspeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.76,0:23:17.68,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,An epidemic to the east?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.68,0:23:20.87,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Medicine's flying off \Nthe shelves, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.20,0:23:26.15,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Where shall we head next, Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.43,0:23:28.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,East.
